Jour: Jour. of Physics, Part A (Mathematical+General), Vol.5, p.1262 (1972)

x4freetext: Same results for Cd-116 but with
Natural elements in metallic powder or oxide form
Activation method plus absolute gamma counting.
Decay half-life was followed for unique identification
Spin cut-off factors deduced using the Huizenga-
Experimental values of the spin cut-off factor are
compared with the predictions of the shifted Fermi-gas
model, independent pairing model and suconductor
VS Reaction code in subent 022 corrected
